title: FNaF World: Scratch Version Solo vs. Bosses (silent jumpscare version)
description:
The jumpscare noise is gone now, because apparently Scratch had this game removed because of what I'm assuming is that the jumpscare noise was too scary or something.

I "made" a reduced-lag version of this game.  However, things that were previously GIFs, such as bosses and characters, will no longer move.  If you still want moving bosses, then read the stuff below.  If not, then use the link here ---> https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/115818356/ to play the reduced-lag game.

I have some good news and some bad news.  The good news is that the game shouldn't lag as much anymore.  The bad news is that to do this, I had to remove a huge amount of the bosses and reduce it to only five.  However, this is just so I can spread the bosses out to other more organized projects.  This, sadly, means that I will no longer be adding characters to the games as well, as this would require me to make the character in each individual project from the ground up.

Music: "FNaF World Title Theme" by Leon Riskin
           "Melting Titanium" by Leon Riskin
           "Wrong Enemy" by Toby "Radiation" Fox
FNaF World Halloween/Leaked/Troll Edition/Fighter Mage Bard Battle Theme by ? (Unknown until further notice)

SFX: BrowBoy's Laugh - Laugh of Nelson from The Simpsons, but lower pitch
        Jumpscare - FNaF 1 Jumpscare

Sprites and FNaF franchise belong to Scott Cawthon.
Simpsons belongs to Matt Groening.
instructions:
Use this link: https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/115818356/
I don't know why people won't use that link.

READ NOTES AND CREDITS!  IMPORTANT!

Click the green flag to start.
When the game starts, choose a character by clicking its icon.
If a character's icon is greyed out (or has a red X over it in the case of the starting 8 characters) then it is under construction and therefore unusable until it is finished.
When the battle starts, click the attack buttons to use the attack that is named.
When you win or lose, click the green flag twice to restart.
For an added challenge, wait for each attack to completely disappear before using another.

title: fnaf rejected custom night
description: thanks to romanatschool i fixed some of the bugs and glitches( there are still bugs im trying to fix )
instructions:
Z- FlashLight / Lanterna


Secret Caracters:

Toy Foxy/Mangle:
Buy his plush toy at the Prize Counter (Cam 07) when she appears in the right hall to avoid her attack! She can't be stopped by the office door. 
Compre o seu brinquedo de pelúcia no balcão de prêmios (Cam 07) quando ela aparecer no corredor certo para evitar seu ataque! Ela não pode ser parada na porta do escritório.

Adventure Endo 01: 
He blocks your vision for a few seconds. 
Ele bloqueia sua visão por alguns segundos.

Adventure Chipper:
See on the cameras which hallway he is in and close the appropriate door.
Veja nas câmeras em que corredor ele está e feche a porta apropriada.

Unwithered Freddy: 
Check the cameras in which corridor he is in and close the appropriate door, but if he enters put on the mask to make him go. 
Veja nas câmeras em que corredor ele está e feche a porta apropriada, mas se ele entrar coloque a mascara para faze-lo ir.

Unwithered Bonnie: 
Put on the mask to make it go.
Coloque a mascara para fazer ele ir.

Unwithered Chica:
She climbs through the air vents, but can get stuck trying to get into her office. Close the vent door when you see her eyes through the opening and wait until it comes out.
Ela sobe pelas saídas de ar, mas pode ficar presa tentando entrar em seu escritório. Feche a porta da ventilação quando você ver os olhos dela na abertura e aguarde até ela sair.

Unwithered Foxy: 
When you hear him running, close the left door, but if he enters, turn his flashlight on him.
Quando você ouvir ele correndo, feche a porta esquerda, mas se ele entrar, ligue sua lanterna nele.
